{"tid":93843,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"金魚街店舖大力擲魚落地 涉嫌虐魚","createTime":"2017-01-24T17:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T16:58:18.000Z","uid":30487,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85775933bbf56169eb376c975edbcf182943418f","tid":93843,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/1488246968058120?view=permalink&amp;id=1865333860349427&amp;refid=18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1488246968058120%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D1865333860349427%26refid%3D18&d=EDGy0AL4hGRsw6pfeBIzd2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=9cdd5863\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/1488246968058120?view=permalink&amp;id=1865333860349427&amp;refid=18</a><br />\n<br />\n事發經過：<br />\n有間魚舖發現新大陸<br />\n以為有款號稱防撞爆嘅裝魚膠袋係新發明<br />\n其實早幾廿年已經有同類產品<br />\n個大陸老mk以為自己好威威啦<br />\n就擺左條魚入去大力掉落地幾次<br />\n個袋當然唔會爛<br />\n但條魚喺入面撞黎撞去<br />\n一定唔會無受傷<br />\n<br />\n涉事魚舖回應：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/010506_33e482d61fc2844b7e638d269117726e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F010506_33e482d61fc2844b7e638d269117726e.jpg&h=3161e850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/010519_180d206246b73f3b7f04b8dd10dd9ab8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F010519_180d206246b73f3b7f04b8dd10dd9ab8.jpg&h=c778ab81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉事大陸老mk：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/kuMaMon1211?fref=ts#!/kuMaMon1211?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FkuMaMon1211%3Ffref%3Dts%23%21%2FkuMaMon1211%3Ffref%3Dts&d=EDGy0AL4hGRsw6pfeBIzd2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=86c04d2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/kuMaMon1211?fref=ts#!/kuMaMon1211?fref=ts</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nz78p09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnz78p09.jpg&h=22b10c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/012408_3e414ad994f9f010b9444e7288f96357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F012408_3e414ad994f9f010b9444e7288f96357.jpg&h=cf5ec73d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哎喲喲咁就打死人啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/012428_c13e16e42e0def7d03efd52b9add10b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F012428_c13e16e42e0def7d03efd52b9add10b7.jpg&h=7b6a543b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/012745_15941784b6eff34efb0d76b350872a27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F012745_15941784b6eff34efb0d76b350872a27.jpg&h=acb6241e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2H5dmQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2H5dmQ.jpg&h=0b61d1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jA0Euf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjA0Euf6.jpg&h=a4c2c6e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ec8696a7d78bfa56e67ed5813af48fcaf897718","tid":93843,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"想買魚囉喎<br />\n咪打呢個電話囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwy57t3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkwy57t3.jpg&h=9d2079fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4101b422dba99ae6928dfa01ff2883df31eef1a","tid":93843,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:37: